{"word":"G736 - ἀρτέμων - artémōn - ar-tem'-ohn - Mainsail","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀρτέμων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">artémōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ar-tem'-ohn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Mainsail</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"பெரும்பாய் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"main - sail"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G737 - ἄρτι - árti - ar'-tee/737\">G737</a>; properly something <i>ready</i> (or else more remotely from <a href=\"#/G142 - αἴρω - aírō - ah'-ee-ro/142\">G142</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G740 - ἄρτος - ártos - ar'-tos/740\">G740</a>); something <i>hung</i> up), that is, (specifically) the <i>topsail</i> (rather <i>foresail</i> or <i>jib</i>) of a vessel: - mainsail.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}